    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and represents a rare find for any discerning buyer. It has been meticulously maintained, stored in a climate-controlled garage, and shows virtually no signs of wear inside or out. The paint retains its original showroom luster, the interior is pristine with no blemishes, and the engine performs flawlessly as if it just rolled off the assembly line. All maintenance records are up to date, and the car drives perfectly with no mechanical or cosmetic issues whatsoever. This is an exceptional example of this model, ideal for a collector or someone who demands the highest quality possible.",
      "price": 48000.0,
